sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Team Leader
    participant FE as React<br/>TeamPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>InviteMemberView
    participant SER as InviteMemberSerializer
    participant Perm as IsTeamLeader
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Enter user email, click "Invite"
    FE->>API: POST /api/environments/{env_id}/invite/ {email}
    API->>Perm: has_permission(request)
    Perm-->>API: Allowed (Team Leader role)
    API->>SER: InviteMemberSerializer.validate(data)
    SER->>DB: CustomUser.objects.get(email=email)
    DB-->>SER: Target user found
    SER-->>API: Validated invite data
    API->>DB: EnvironmentMembership.objects.create(user, env, role="member")
    DB-->>API: Membership created
    API-->>FE: 201 Created {membership}
    FE-->>U: User added to team members list
